{"tid":2397792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple將Asian列為成人詞語 其他地域不受影響","createTime":"2021-02-06T17:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T03:20:46.000Z","uid":49004,"like":32,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3190f5baca147621a5d32f6f994bc7d926464521","tid":2397792,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:25:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/02/06/gadgets-and-tech-apple-adult-filter-asian-iphone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F02%2F06%2Fgadgets-and-tech-apple-adult-filter-asian-iphone%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=7c5d1d56\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/02/06/gadgets-and-tech-apple-adult-filter-asian-iphone/</a><br />\nApple 將 Asian 列為成人詞語 其他地域不受影響<br />\n<br />\n網上有害資訊不少，對於家長而言要保護小孩不受這些資訊影響也不容易。Apple 在 iOS 14 加入了內容管制功能，但就有報導指 Apple 將「Asian」列為成人詞語，開啓內容管制功能之後無法搜尋這些關鍵字。<br />\n<br />\n這個內容管制功能會偵測禁用字，開啓之後在 Safari 會無法搜尋相關的關鍵字。報導指，「Asian」不知為什麼被列為成人詞語，連帶所有與「Asian」相關的關鍵字都無法搜尋，包括「Asian Food」、「Asian Culture」等等，唯一例外是「Asian Restaurants」但原因不明。其他的地域例如「Indian」、「African」等等都不受影響。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/EtTsm__UYAUM9R7.jfif_-1280x894.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FEtTsm__UYAUM9R7.jfif_-1280x894.jpeg&h=b3c19437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApple 方面並沒有公佈禁用字列表，或者他們判斷成人詞語的方針。有趣的是，在 macOS 的 Safari 上開啓內容管制功能的話，「Asian」就可以正常搜尋。<br />\n<br />\n來源：Independent<br />\n<br />\nAsian<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d975d7ec69b3a46b84cb31577fbfd3c64d0e88a5","tid":2397792,"uid":198952,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:26:56.000Z","msg":"以後拜登就可以光明正大食asian妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656b96073a083f7964b16c1532d3d1dafa8ae92c","tid":2397792,"uid":301989,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:29:01.000Z","msg":"asian lives matter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9eeb8b7179adcc8dd1e8b97884e2bf418d65e80","tid":2397792,"uid":253016,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Asian=幼幼"},{"pid":"4a4fdd73e1d7bc94400e4c5df971818551a0d403","tid":2397792,"uid":48362,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"這杯水想強姦我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a18cd116e09fb56a98d8dad07a24ccf7b905cdd","tid":2397792,"uid":55458,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T21:27:52.000Z","msg":"asian啲閪特別窄<br />\n屌得特別爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7744b6835f3a4121a1382789f330810dc99932c4","tid":2397792,"uid":141917,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T21:41:39.000Z","msg":"二等公民"},{"pid":"d753d13ec385e244400b1104a99fc74fb081d96e","tid":2397792,"uid":23061,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T21:44:58.000Z","msg":"真係多謝晒左翼成功爭取啊<img src=\"/